## Our roadmap as of now :

The version number represents the targeted objectives to be accomplished in the final iteration of the release.

We may occasionally incorporate new features and improvements into stable branches if they're feasible and beneficial to the existing codebase. The decision depends on factors like complexity and relevance to the stable version.

