## Forward Looking

* Implement more sophisticated UI detection model.
* Improve frame generation output and find the balance between performance, quality and power consumption.

## Possibly in the future?

* Termux X11 Support
* Upscaling? Post-Processing?
* No root mode (A11+)

Keep in mind that these list are non-exhaustive, there are maybe even more caveats and to-dos that we haven't discovered yet along with the **unknown possibility** of such thing to be implemented. We will still try to mitigate any issues through potential workarounds where feasible.

This roadmap may change at any moment.

